home.slogan: More than just a nightclub, Eclipse is an experience!
home.marquee: The best DJs – Guest artist line-ups – Themed parties – VIP areas – Stage
home.club: At Eclipse, the night comes alive with the best music and entertainment. Enjoy our guest DJs, a unique show featuring dancers, and exclusive VIP areas for an unforgettable experience. Feel the adrenaline of our themed parties, with special effects like CO₂ cannons that take the energy to the next level. Eclipse is where music, atmosphere, and fun come together for a night like no other.
